  <description><![CDATA[<p>The Magic Hotel Kloverhuset is situated in central Bergen, right near the waterfront and only a short stroll to Bergen's fish market.</p>
<h2>Perfectly positioned</h2>
<p>Location doesn't get much better. With the famous, UNESCO heritage listed site, Bryggen, right opposite the hotel, wander over and explore the little streets around Bergen's historic harbour. The light rail is only around 10 minutes walk from the hotel but if you're wanting some great views over Bergen then journey up in the funicular to Mount Floyen.</p>
<h2>A hotel with style</h2>
<p>The sophisticated hotel entrance and reception area are situated by the bar and restaurant, with wine bottles being the main décor feature. The rooms, offer modern and contemporary design that create a calming space.</p>]]></description>
