  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Twin Rooms</strong> sleep up to two guests, and are made up of two single beds.</p>
<p><strong>Single Rooms</strong> are cosy and offer a single bed.</p>
<p><strong>Junior Suites</strong> or rooms for three people are all available on a request basis and at an extra charge. Please call to book.</p>
<p><strong>All rooms have:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>TV</li>
<li>Hairdryer</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>General information </strong></p>
<p>Check in: 3pm<br />Check out: 12pm</p>
